 (8.2)]. Infertility Inform patients that treatment with cisplatin for injection may lead to permanent impairment of spermatogenesis, ovarian failure or premature menopause, and reduced fertility in both genders [see Use in Specific Populations (8.3)]. Alopecia Inform patients that cisplatin for injection can cause alopecia. Manufactured for: WG Critical Care, LLC Paramus, NJ 07652 Made in Italy"
